{"tid":1320102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真心一問 究竟呢個局面可以點拆","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:25:44.000Z","uid":183762,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d75ded101d744f04145169272a53c1e7bd40b8","tid":1320102,"uid":183762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:04:09.000Z","msg":"睇完吳志森段片 有d心寒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5TcqC5-Wq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx5TcqC5-Wq4&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=bcdb00b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5TcqC5-Wq4</a><br />\n<br />\n宜家政府擺明比警察同市民放係敵對既局面<br />\n<br />\n萬一警察比人打死左 就可以令民意扭轉 警察亦可以出師有名用真槍鎮壓示威者<br />\n呢個係唯一解釋到點解旺角或者今次沙田要玩困獸鬥 宜家大家仇警情緒咁高漲 警察又當正市民係敵人 再落去一定雙方都會有傷亡 <br />\n<br />\n我真心覺得政府今次係要搞到有人死先肯收手 我唔係左膠 我都好憎警察<br />\n但我真係唸唔到宜家可以點拆"},{"pid":"8fe2980e60c35f44afe88efcb204dc7c1241fd07","tid":1320102,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"296ac0ca80626cde16f6df79f42f563eb0fbd181","tid":1320102,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"點解你地嘅三毛硬係覺得有隻狗死咗就會民意逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd63b78145e2dede9a214df28607118673ff0968","tid":1320102,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320014/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320014/page/1</a><br />\n狗狗聽主人唔同指令實在好大壓力，應該就來爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候搵傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5827aa5b7790993b54c7267b5fc463c61dba665b","tid":1320102,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"正苦只會再一次錯判形勢"},{"pid":"cfefa4e6fe4290a99825b67d5bd5ea7de72e22a3","tid":1320102,"uid":57549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"做齊5大訴求就可以解決"},{"pid":"f7456816e0cafeccb5f8da987481fb33c212b350","tid":1320102,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"只會由政府諗<br />\n<br />\n但佢地可能唔明<br />\n和理非同勇武果班變左一體後<br />\n依個water仲湧緊向國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3fae9a695644cb15083f412506fd0fa62ebd6a","tid":1320102,"uid":50366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"發夢見到有人講<br />\n想再信返班差佬<br />\n佢地一定要解甲投降，重要自切揸警棍同開鎗果隻手<br />\n咁就真係夠曬誠意和解"},{"pid":"c19fa50bee874de6101cd26e34b3ea966a045127","tid":1320102,"uid":240788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"屌可唔可以一齊屌鳩呢啲濕鳩page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4045677dff94ec3b35d26ab480d6e1d780aaba0c","tid":1320102,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"6月頭講撒回就乜事都冇"},{"pid":"b2418c0044b63001d5c82d3116bc3c51003e5bec","tid":1320102,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"願意代抗爭者一死先，避免扭轉局面<br />\n但點樣可以確保比黑警打死而唔係比佢拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d936cbd6786ed55c3c5163647806d691459d1a03","tid":1320102,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"我會無時無刻一得閒就推呢個post<br />\n以防有手足以為警察會倒戈而心軟<br />\n<br />\n沒有一個警案是無辜的<br />\n而家打緊仗<br />\n對敵人仁慈就即係棄自己手足安危於不顧"},{"pid":"9ca91f78322c7b7fb0bd0d3a92b7c471c46d9b38","tid":1320102,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"「萬一警察比人打死左 就可以令民意扭轉 警察亦可以出師有名用真槍鎮壓示威者」<br />\n擔心咁多都冇用啦<br />\n如果到時民意真係逆轉都冇辦法<br />\n而且我都幾肯定就算有人死 政府都唔會收手<br />\n而家應該期望美國盡快推動民主人權法案"},{"pid":"974fd96a38b0eb931a966578da141bbabfd3c1f4","tid":1320102,"uid":185877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實點解呢個時候仲會在呼民意？你係咪on9?"},{"pid":"c55a2a00dcb5d4f9e626ca2a97eab7539a77220f","tid":1320102,"uid":269280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"唔好比警民衝突令到運動失焦！依家每次遊行示威咋都係不反對通知書expire之前俾警察包抄圍毆拘捕，然後鏡頭影到示威者自衛就話我哋打警察，林鄭同一哥就施施然出嚟譴責示威者同追究被捕人士，完成整個劇本。五大訴求無人回應。係時候再次be water, 轉陣了！創意示威、控告整個警隊、超合作運動、打民意戰同選舉工程等。仲有冇其他ideas？"},{"pid":"e835f6aff3b530ff5c7994a21efa7bbfeecb890f","tid":1320102,"uid":183762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4045677dff94ec3b35d26ab480d6e1d780aaba0c","tid":1320102,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"6月頭講撒回就乜事都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"錯曬時間啦 6月第一次游行已經要跪 仲要死不認錯 咪搞到今日咁既局面"},{"pid":"0e01c739ad15aa9877b9088ed188838716e4eb9f","tid":1320102,"uid":183762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974fd96a38b0eb931a966578da141bbabfd3c1f4","tid":1320102,"uid":185877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實點解呢個時候仲會在呼民意？你係咪on9?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"我唔應該咁講 但宜家次次都例牌演變成警民衝突 五大訴求一樣都無回應過 再落去一定有死傷 宜家兩邊都越黎越激 我有d擔心"}]}